---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact | YWAM Sendai" lang="en">
  <main class="bg-dark-bg text-white">
    <section class="px-6 pt-28 pb-16 md:pt-36 md:pb-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] block mb-5">Start Here</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif italic text-white mb-6">Contact</h1>
        <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg">
          Questions, next steps, or just want to connect? Here are the simplest ways to begin.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <button
            class="open-hub-trigger px-6 py-5 bg-gold-accent text-black font-black rounded-full hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform uppercase tracking-widest text-xs cursor-pointer"
          >
            Ask AI
          </button>

          <a
            href="#message-us"
            class="px-6 py-5 border border-zinc-700 text-white rounded-full hover:border-gold-accent hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-xs flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            Message Us
          </a>

          <a
            href="/en/apply"
            class="px-6 py-5 border border-zinc-700 text-white rounded-full hover:border-gold-accent hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-xs flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            Apply
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 pb-12 md:pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-white">Ask AI</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Best for quick questions about DTS, DBS, applications, contact, or the handbook.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-white">Message Us</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Best for first contact, personal questions, or ongoing connection with the community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-white">Apply</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            Best for students, staff, outreach teams, guests, or visitors ready for a concrete next step.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="message-us" class="px-6 py-12 md:py-16 bg-zinc-950">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mb-10">
          <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] block mb-4">Message Us</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif italic text-white mb-4">Choose the easiest way to connect</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
            Messaging apps are often the easiest first step, especially for younger people and casual questions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
          <div class="bg-dark-bg border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-serif italic mb-2">Discord</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              Best for community, first connection, and staying in touch over time.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://discord.gg/djmCF4DBaV"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="mt-auto inline-block text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8 hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest"
            >
              Join Discord
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-bg border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-serif italic mb-2">LINE</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              Best for Japanese-language inquiries.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://lin.ee/LD2Nf4b"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="mt-auto inline-block text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8 hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest"
            >
              Message on LINE
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-bg border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-serif italic mb-2">Instagram</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              Best for informal questions and simple first contact.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://ig.me/m/ywamsendai"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="mt-auto inline-block text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8 hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest"
            >
              Message on Instagram
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-bg border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-6 flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-serif italic mb-2">Email</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
              If you prefer email, you can reach us at hello@ywamsendai.org.
            </p>
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@ywamsendai.org"
              class="mt-auto inline-block text-xs font-bold underline underline-offset-8 hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest"
            >
              Email Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-7">
          <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] block mb-4">Concrete Next Step</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif italic text-white mb-4">Ready to apply?</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base mb-5">
            If you want to apply as a student or staff member, ask about an outreach team, or inquire about a guest stay, the application form is usually the best place to begin.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/en/apply"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-4 bg-gold-accent text-black font-black rounded-full hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform uppercase tracking-widest text-xs"
          >
            Go to Application Form
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-zinc-900/60 border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2rem] p-7">
          <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] block mb-4">Before You Message</span>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif italic text-white mb-4">Helpful to include</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            <li>• your name</li>
            <li>• the reason for contacting</li>
            <li>• any relevant dates or timing</li>
            <li>• your main question</li>
            <li>• any important background information</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="px-6 pb-20 md:pb-28">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center border border-zinc-800 rounded-[2.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 bg-zinc-950">
        <span class="text-gold-accent text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.35em] block mb-4">Need More Detail?</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif italic text-white mb-4">Still exploring?</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto text-sm md:text-base mb-8">
          You can ask the AI a question or visit the online handbook for more detailed information.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
          <button
            class="open-hub-trigger px-6 py-4 bg-gold-accent text-black font-black rounded-full hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform uppercase tracking-widest text-xs cursor-pointer"
          >
            Ask AI
          </button>
          <a
            href="https://guide.ywamsendai.org"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="px-6 py-4 border border-zinc-700 text-white rounded-full hover:border-gold-accent hover:text-gold-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-xs"
          >
            Visit Handbook
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>